oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Thomas Maupin competes in dance competition at Uncle Dave Macon Days
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Champion buckdancer Thomas Maupin of Murfreesboro, TN, competes in the dance competition at Uncle Dave Macon Days, Rutherford Co., TN, 1987.
Maupin is a 2011 Tennessee Folklife Heritage Award recipient.
